B.a2z=new A.m(B.w,"Modal + Fiil Yap\u0131s\u0131",'**Rule:** Modal verb + **base infinitive** (no "to", no "-s", no "-ing")\n\n\u2713 The pilot **must check** the fuel level.\n\u2717 The pilot must **checks** / must **checking** / must **to check**\n\n**With passive:**\nModal + **be** + past participle\n\u2713 The engine **must be shut down** before maintenance.\n\u2713 Parts **should be inspected** visually.',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
