B.a09=new A.m(B.w,"\ud83d\udd27 Hidrolik & \u0130ni\u015f Tak\u0131m\u0131","**Hydraulic actuator** \u2014 converts hydraulic pressure to mechanical movement\n**Hydraulic pump** \u2014 pressurizes hydraulic fluid\n**Landing gear strut** \u2014 shock-absorbing leg of landing gear\n**Torque link** \u2014 scissors linkage preventing wheel rotation on strut\n**Brake assembly** \u2014 disc brakes on main landing gear wheels",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
