B.a1H=new A.m(B.z,"Readback nedir?","**Readback** (geri okuma), ATC talimatlar\u0131n\u0131n pilotlar taraf\u0131ndan tam olarak tekrar edilmesidir. ICAO standartlar\u0131na g\xf6re a\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki bilgiler mutlaka readback yap\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r:\n\n\u2022 Pist numaras\u0131 (kalk\u0131\u015f/ini\u015f izinleri dahil)\n\u2022 Y\xf6n ve y\xfckseklik talimatlar\u0131\n\u2022 Transponder kodlar\u0131\n\u2022 R\xfczgar bilgisi ile birlikte verilen kalk\u0131\u015f izinleri\n\u2022 Pist ge\xe7i\u015f talimatlar\u0131",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.a_k=new A.m(B.w,"Readback Kurallar\u0131",'**DO readback (mutlaka tekrar et):**\n\u2022 ATC clearances (route, altitude, heading)\n\u2022 Runway crossing/entry instructions\n\u2022 Takeoff and landing clearances\n\u2022 QNH / altimeter settings\n\u2022 Frequency changes\n\n**Format:** [Talimat i\xe7eri\u011fi] + [Callsign]\n\xd6rnek: "Descend to 3000 feet, QNH 1018, TK1234."\n\n**Readback vermek yeterlili\u011fi onaylar** \u2014 yanl\u0131\u015f anla\u015f\u0131lmay\u0131 \xf6nler.',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
