B.a1C=new A.m(B.aw,"\u2708\ufe0f S\u0131nav \u0130pucu",'Prosed\xfcr belgelerinde "At or above" / "at or below":\n\u2022 "A030+" = 3.000 ft veya **\xfczeri** (art\u0131 i\u015fareti = daha y\xfcksek)\n\u2022 "A050-" = 5.000 ft veya **alt\u0131** (eksi i\u015fareti = daha al\xe7ak)\n\nBir ara noktada hem h\u0131z hem irtifa k\u0131s\u0131tlamas\u0131 varsa, **her ikisine** e\u015f zamanl\u0131 uyulmal\u0131d\u0131r.\n\nBir STAR\'daki "Expect vectors", ATC\'nin her zaman vekt\xf6r verece\u011fi anlam\u0131na gelmez \u2014 pilot beklemelidir (vekt\xf6r verilmezse yay\u0131mlanm\u0131\u015f prosed\xfcr\xfc uygulay\u0131n).',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
