B.Th=new A.a1('"Pilots are encouraged to file occurrence reports under the just culture framework without fear of punitive action."',"Pilotlar cezaland\u0131rma korkusu olmadan adaletli k\xfclt\xfcr \xe7er\xe7evesinde olay raporlar\u0131 doldurmaya te\u015fvik edilmektedir.","occurrence reports \u2026 just culture \u2026 without fear of punitive action")
