B.a0P=new A.m(B.z,"U\xe7u\u015f \xd6ncesi Teknik Teslim","Bak\u0131m i\u015flemi sonras\u0131nda teknisyen, u\xe7a\u011f\u0131 **certify** ederek kaptana **release** (teslim) eder. Bu s\xfcre\xe7te:\n\n\u2022 Yap\u0131lan i\u015f a\xe7\u0131k\xe7a tarif edilir\n\u2022 Herhangi bir **limitation** (k\u0131s\u0131tlama) varsa bildirilir\n\u2022 **Certificate of Release to Service (CRS)** verilir\n\nKaptan teknik g\xfcnl\xfc\u011f\xfc (technical log) imzalamadan \xf6nce sorular\u0131 sorabilir.",null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
B.Qe=new A.bS(B.eZ,"Good morning, Captain. I'm the certifying engineer. I need to brief you on the maintenance carried out overnight.","G\xfcnayd\u0131n Kaptan. Ben sertifika m\xfchendisiyim. Geceyi kapsayan bak\u0131m hakk\u0131nda sizi bilgilendirmem gerekiyor.",!1)
