B.UF=new A.a1("All passengers must evacuate the aircraft immediately. Leave all hand baggage behind and proceed to the nearest exit.","T\xfcm yolcular u\xe7aktan derhal tahliye edilmelidir. T\xfcm el bagajlar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 geride b\u0131rak\u0131n ve en yak\u0131n \xe7\u0131k\u0131\u015fa do\u011fru ilerleyin.","Leave all hand baggage behind")
