B.a2T=new A.m(B.w,"Crew Rest Terminolojisi",'**Crew rest compartment (CRC)** \u2014 ekip dinlenme b\xf6lmesi (\xfcst veya alt g\xfcverte)\n**Break schedule** \u2014 dinlenme takvimi\n**In-charge cabin crew member** \u2014 sorumlu kabin amiri\n\n\u0130fadeler:\n"I\'m going on my scheduled break. [Name] will be in charge."\n"Please call me if there is a medical emergency or if turbulence is forecast."\n"The crew will be taking turns resting. One senior crew member will remain in the cabin at all times."\n"We are approximately [X] hours from destination. Crew rest will begin shortly."',null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
